name: Tiki Tiki Mini Golf
description:
Play the latest Tiki Mini Golf game created on Coppercube 6.5.1. Try to get the golf ball into the pocket before the timer runs out, in order to complete the game. 

CONTROL+

WASD MOVEMENT

W BUTTON: Gives automatic swing movement to the club.

Press 1: Reset game as many times as you want.

3 Minute Timer
